<plot>Winner of the 2004 HBO Short Film Award at the American Black Film Festival, TIME OUT offers a chapter in the life of Lauren Martin, a precocious nine-year old dealing with life after the lost of her mother. A confrontation with a jealous classmate triggers a domino effect which eventually puts her face to face with a decision that will forever change the road on which she must choose to follow.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?608471</url></doc>
